tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE UserInteractions ( 
 interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
 user_id UUID, 
 assistant_id UUID, 
 interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ, 
 interaction_text TEXT, 
 interaction_type TEXT 
 );

CREATE TABLE UserInteractions (
    InteractionID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    UserID INT,
    AssistantType VARCHAR(255),
    InteractionTime TIMESTAMP,
    InteractionDuration INT
);

CREATE TABLE AIAlgorithms (
    AlgorithmID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    AlgorithmName VARCHAR(255),
    AlgorithmType VARCHAR(255),
    CreationDate DATE,
    Accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    assistant_id INT,
    interaction_datetime TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_text TEXT
);
CREATE TABLE UserInteractions (user_id INT, interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP, interaction_text TEXT)
CREATE TABLE AssistantInteractions (assistant_id INT, interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP, user_id INT, interaction_text TEXT)
CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (interaction_id INT, user_id INT, feedback_score INT)
CREATE TABLE AssistantFeedback (interaction_id INT, assistant_id INT, feedback_comments TEXT)

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    voice_command TEXT NOT NULL,
    assistant_response TEXT,
    interaction_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_accounts (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    password_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    profile_picture BYTEA
);

CREATE TABLE assistant_logs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id INT NOT NULL,
    assistant_id INT NOT NULL,
    log_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    log_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE interaction_metadata (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    assistant_id INT NOT NULL,
    session_id INT NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(100)
);
